---
title: Bravo Balsamic Steak with Roasted Green Beans & Herby Potatoes
description: Another work day, another dinner daydream. You know what we mean. You’re sitting at your desk and 2:00 pm rolls around. Suddenly, all you can think is, “Dinner... what the heck am I going to eat for dinner?!” Well, we’ve got you covered, and FYI, the answer to that question is pretty delicious. We’re serving up pan-seared chicken with roasted Brussels sprouts and garlic-herb potatoes. To finish things off, the chicken is drizzled with a life-affirming rosemary balsamic pan sauce. Talk about a dream come true!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bravo-balsamic-steak-bb924bc5.jpg
